description:
John Schreiber, President & CEO, New Jersey Performing Arts Center talks about the great line-up of guests that we have for our second annual taping of “One-on-One” at Newark’s NJPAC.

Christian McBride, Bassist, Composer, Arranger and Educator talks about his love of jazz, the talented musicians he has worked with over his 20 year career, and his two new CD’s that just released.

Dorthaan Kirk, Special Events & Community Relations Coordinator, Newark Public Radio – WBGO Jazz 88.3FM talks about her involvement with NJPAC through WBGO’s Kids Jazz Concert Series and ‘Dorthaan’s Place’.

12/10/13
